      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(ui): reload WebChat history for deferred thinking",
        "body": "Fixes #91727.\n\n## Summary\n\nWebChat now reloads the selected transcript at the end of a run when a deferred persisted `session.message` already contains assistant thinking/reasoning but the live final chat payload only contains renderable answer text. That restores the post-run repaint that makes persisted reasoning visible without a manual browser refresh, while preserving the no-reload path for normal source-reply finals.\n\n## Root cause\n\nThe final chat-event path avoided `loadChatHistory()` whenever a terminal final event carried renderable assistant text, even if an earlier `session.message` during the same active run had the persisted assistant message with thinking content. That meant the live UI kept the final text payload and never re-projected the transcript thinking block until the user manually refreshed.\n\n## What changed\n\n- Track whether a deferred, selected assistant `session.message` contains thinking content while a chat run is active.\n- Treat a final event as needing history reload when that deferred transcript thinking is missing from the final live payload.\n- Keep the scope tight to the selected/equivalent session and selected agent/global alias so stale or cross-session finals do not reload the visible chat.\n- Ignore user messages that contain literal thinking-like text.\n- Preserve the existing source-reply no-flicker path when there is no deferred transcript thinking to recover.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior or issue addressed: a persisted assistant message containing a `thinking` block arrives via `session.message` during an active WebChat run, then the terminal `chat` final event carries only renderable assistant text. Before this fix, the final payload stayed live and the thinking block remained hidden until a manual refresh. After this fix, the final event calls `loadChatHistory()` once and the selected chat state is replaced with the persisted transcript containing the thinking block.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw source checkout at PR head `260f6a5aec349889942965d24a76fe687efd3818` on macOS using the repo Node/pnpm toolchain. The focused proof drives the real Control UI gateway event handlers with mocked gateway events: `session.message` with persisted assistant thinking followed by the live `chat` final payload.\n\nExact steps or commands run after this patch:\n\n```text\npnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 ui/src/ui/app-gateway.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts\ngit diff --check\nOPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm run check:changed\n```\n\nEvidence after fix:\n\n```text\n$ pnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 ui/src/ui/app-gateway.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts\nAll matched files use the correct format.\n\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts\nTest Files  2 passed (2)\nTests  78 passed (78)\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 1.42s\n\n$ OPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm run check:changed\n[check:changed] lanes=core, coreTests\n[check:changed] ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts: core test\n[check:changed] ui/src/ui/app-gateway.ts: core production\n[check:changed] ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts: core test\n[check:changed] ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.ts: core production\nPASS direct dependency pin guard: checked 467 directly declared dependency specs across 156 tracked package manifests; 0 violations.\nPASS package patch guard: no new pnpm patches; 4 legacy patches allowlisted.\nruntime-sidecar-loaders: local runtime sidecar loaders look OK.\nImport cycle check: 0 runtime value cycle(s).\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: The focused UI test `reloads deferred transcript thinking after a renderable final assistant payload` verifies `loadChatHistory()` is called exactly once, the selected `chatMessages` become `[persistedUser, persistedAssistant]`, and `persistedAssistant` includes `{ type: \"thinking\", thinking: \"private reasoning\" }`. The tool-backed final variant also reloads and clears the tool stream after history reload, while cross-session/user-message guard tests do not reload.\n\nWhat was not tested: I did not run a live external provider WebChat session because the local proof does not require model credentials and isolates the UI event path named in the reporter's correction.\n\n## Validation\n\n```text\npnpm exec oxfmt --check --threads=1 ui/src/ui/app-gateway.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts\nnode scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/chat-event-reload.test.ts ui/src/ui/app-gateway.node.test.ts\ngit diff --check\nOPENCLAW_CHECK_CHANGED_REMOTE_CHILD=1 OPENCLAW_CHANGED_LANES_RAW_SYNC=1 CI=1 PNPM_CONFIG_VERIFY_DEPS_BEFORE_RUN=false pnpm run check:changed\ngit log --format='%h %an <%ae> %s' upstream/main..HEAD\n```\n\nCommit author verification:\n\n```text\n260f6a5aec Andy Ye <35905412+TurboTheTurtle@users.noreply.github.com> fix(ui): reload webchat history for deferred thinking\n```\n\nOpen PR overlap checked before publishing: direct `#91727` search returned no open PRs. Broader WebChat/reasoning searches found adjacent stream-delivery/sanitization PRs (#87481, #79687, #90924, #90186) but no open PR covering the final history reload path for #91727.\n",
